OL,3,C90% of retailers not providing legal
OL,4,Crequirement vape recycling points
OL,6,FVape retailers who don't take back e-
OL,7,Fcigs are breaking the law, ITV News'
OL,8,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,10,FA big problem with disposable is where
OL,11,Fthey are disposed.
OL,13,FNow, there are warnings that there's a
OL,14,Flot more litter to come - despite an
OL,15,Fimpending ban on single-use .
OL,17,FNew research given to ITV News by
OL,18,Frecycling experts Material Focus
OL,19,Fsuggest that 250 million single use
OL,20,Fvapes will be thrown away before they
OL,21,Fare banned.
