OL,3,C90% of retailers not providing legal
OL,4,Crequirement vape recycling points
OL,6,FThat's expected to happen in April
OL,7,F2025 for most of the UK.
OL,9,F360 million are sold each year, and
OL,10,Ffive million thrown away every week.
OL,12,FVape retailers who don't take back e-
OL,13,Fcigs are breaking the law, yet
OL,14,FMaterial Focus researchers in 13
OL,15,Fcities claim many outlets refused.
OL,17,FOne outlet that I tried told me to put
OL,18,Fmy used vape in the bin, but that's
OL,19,Fnot a good idea because they have
OL,20,Fcaused fires in the waste disposal
OL,21,Fchain.
