OL,3,C90% of retailers not providing legal
OL,4,Crequirement vape recycling points
OL,6,FAll the big retail chains we spoke to
OL,7,Fsay they do recycle vapes and tell
OL,8,Fcustomers about it with signs near
OL,9,Fcheckout - but clearly staff don't
OL,10,Falways know about these policies.
OL,12,FWe put these findings to John Dunne of
OL,13,FUK Vaping Industry Association.
OL,15,FHe told us: "It's really important for
OL,16,Fgovernment agencies to work together
OL,17,Fto come up with solutions that really
OL,18,Fwork.
