OL,3,C90% of retailers not providing legal
OL,4,Crequirement vape recycling points
OL,6,F"Every retailer who sells these
OL,7,Fproducts should be providing the
OL,8,Ffacilities to recycle."
OL,10,FThe retail sector insists it is
OL,11,Frolling out vape take back schemes.
OL,13,FBut designated recycling bins are not
OL,14,Fa legal requirement and campaigners
OL,15,Ffear there's a lot more of this litter
OL,16,Fto come.
