OL,6,FScott Butler of Material Focus, a non-
OL,7,Fprofit environmental organisation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's a pollutant, you've got
OL,9,Fnicotine liquid in there with damage
OL,10,Fto land, to waterways and to wildlife.
OL,12,F"We also hear stories of cars running
OL,13,Fover vapes and them catching fire so
OL,14,Ftyres burst."
